{"tid":1701294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人會唔會太好","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T04:32:08.000Z","uid":203986,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc562b4e3204c676228efb9ec787151ba58194a4","tid":1701294,"uid":203986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"原本係到等緊巴士，無啦啦有兩個女人過嚟比咗啲散子我，叫我唔好用八達通，話驚有危險。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我認為佢都係有散子多，然後比啲我啦。<br />\n之後我上車嗰陣佢仲沖左過嚟，問我係唔係會去發夢，仲攞咗張$500出嚟，係咁同我講「係唔係無飯食啊，收左佢買飯食啦。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當堂嚇一跳，本能反應咁舉高雙手猛咁rejecte佢同埋沖上架巴士。<br />\n我想講真係好多謝你哋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，細佬未至於發夢發到無飯開，一定有人更加需要呢啲錢。不過你哋份心意真係好warm啊，多謝晒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3449ccdb2e51453ec49ccc3997ecd5300aa915c","tid":1701294,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EI4O4FlXUAExENh?format=jpg&amp;name=4096x4096\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEI4O4FlXUAExENh%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D4096x4096&h=cbcd9b67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ca60a966da26ffe36931084f56105fbb26d6bc6","tid":1701294,"uid":61485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:19:02.000Z","msg":"真係好怕你地食唔飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950e8878516e83915d9bec2a3a36f002d36a8f59","tid":1701294,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"好感動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824ff2e75de0063dfdb63c6d9a4be304c74a9b41","tid":1701294,"uid":271497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T04:32:08.000Z","msg":"Agger 啲錢留比同屋企人反左面既手足啦<br />\n雖然我使哂錢 起碼屋企有飯開先<br />\n上次個兩位手足多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我無錢撘的士走既時候 一人比左兩舊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}